	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
</tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>CHAIN NEED NOT APPLY</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Alan replied to a question from a confused rogue regarding the Velious helmet trade ins. The rogue was curious if this also applied to quested chain helms. Alan stated that unfortunatly, this change was only for the plate helms and if no information was given by the quest NPC then there is no trade in. 	</font>
<br><br><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Click <a href='viewarticle.asp?Article=3383'><b>here</b></a> for details.</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:kivlan@castersrealm.com'>Kivlan</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 4:09 AM</span></p></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
