	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
</tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>SERVER ECONOMICS 101</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Continuing the discussion about server economics, Absor replied to some comments from players on the Developer's Corner discussion board. The comments included Absor's view on item decay as well as server inflation, but he also stated that there aren't likely to be any changes for the economy soon. 	</font>
<br><br><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Click <a href='viewarticle.asp?Article=3382'><b>here</b></a> for details.</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:kivlan@castersrealm.com'>Kivlan</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 4:07 AM</span></p></td>
