	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
</tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>STACKING WITH TRADESKILLS</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>After a certain player noticed a flaw with the new trade container changes, Alan made a post to the Developer's Forum. He warned players that a flaw with the system is that stacked items will be treated as a single stack when dealing with valid recipies, thus you still must be a little careful. 	</font>
<br><br><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Click <a href='viewarticle.asp?Article=3381'><b>here</b></a> for details.</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:kivlan@castersrealm.com'>Kivlan</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 4:03 AM</span></p></td>
