	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
</tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>PVP AND MORE</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>A player submitted a comment to the Developer's Corner regarding the relation of the new PvP server and the discussions regarding a Role-Playing server. Absor responded, stating that there was no relation with the RP server discussions and the new PvP server. He also disclosed that no further progression on the new rule set had been completed, as it was still being discussed. 	</font>
<br><br><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Click <a href='viewarticle.asp?Article=3380'><b>here</b></a> for details.</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:kivlan@castersrealm.com'>Kivlan</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 4:00 AM</span></p></td>
